As previously announced, Eminem has revealed a video for “River” featuring Ed Sheeran in time for Valentine’s Day. A teaser released on Tuesday revealed both the rapper and Sheeran being interviewed about their feelings on love, and that footage can be seen in the first 30 seconds of the final cut. When the music starts, Sheeran is found singing in an empty room, and Eminem, too, raps on his own, as scenes of domestic struggle play out. -Relaxnews